    <div id="app"><div class="min-h-screen bg-gray-900 text-white overflow-x-hidden"><nav class="fixed top-0 w-full z-50 bg-gray-900/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-gray-800"><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="flex justify-between items-center h-16"><a class="flex items-center space-x-2" href="/" data-discover="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-car h-8 w-8 text-purple-400" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M19 17h2c.6 0 1-.4 1-1v-3c0-.9-.7-1.7-1.5-1.9C18.7 10.6 16 10 16 10s-1.3-1.4-2.2-2.3c-.5-.4-1.1-.7-1.8-.7H5c-.6 0-1.1.4-1.4.9l-1.4 2.9A3.7 3.7 0 0 0 2 12v4c0 .6.4 1 1 1h2"></path><circle cx="7" cy="17" r="2"></circle><path d="M9 17h6"></path><circle cx="17" cy="17" r="2"></circle></svg><span class="text-xl font-bold">CarAPI.dev</span></a><div class="hidden md:flex space-x-8"><a href="#features" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white transition-colors">API Services</a><a href="#pricing" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white transition-colors">Pricing</a><a href="https://docs.carapi.dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white transition-colors">Docs</a></div><div class="relative flex items-center space-x-4"><a class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white transition-colors" href="/signin" data-discover="true">Sign In</a><a class="bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-700 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition-all duration-200 hover:scale-105" href="/signup" data-discover="true">Sign Up</a></div></div></div></nav><section class="pt-32 pb-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto"><div class="text-center transform transition-all duration-1000 translate-y-0 opacity-100"><div class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 bg-purple-900/30 border border-purple-800/50 rounded-full px-4 py-2 mb-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-zap h-4 w-4 text-purple-400" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z"></path></svg><span class="text-sm text-purple-300">Trusted by 10,000+ developers</span></div><h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6"><span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-400 via-pink-400 to-blue-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Automotive</span><br>Data API</h1><p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed">Comprehensive automotive data API for VIN decoding, license plate lookup, vehicle listings, and photos. Build automotive applications with reliable, real-time data.</p><div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center"><a href="https://carapi.dev/dashboard" class="group bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-pink-600 hover:from-purple-700 hover:to-pink-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold transition-all duration-200 hover:scale-105 flex items-center justify-center space-x-2"><span>Get API Key</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg></a><a href="https://docs.carapi.dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="border border-gray-700 hover:border-gray-600 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-gray-800/50 inline-block">API Documentation</a></div></div></div></section><section id="features" class="py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-gray-800/50"><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto"><div class="text-center mb-16"><h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Comprehensive Automotive APIs</h2><p class="text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Everything you need to build automotive applications with accurate, up-to-date vehicle data</p></div><div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8"><div class="group p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-700 hover:border-purple-500/50 bg-gray-800/30 hover:bg-gray-800/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105"><div class="text-purple-400 mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-file-text h-8 w-8" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7Z"></path><path d="M14 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4"></path><path d="M10 9H8"></path><path d="M16 13H8"></path><path d="M16 17H8"></path></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">VIN Decode</h3><p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Decode any VIN to get comprehensive vehicle specifications, history, and technical details.</p></div><div class="group p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-700 hover:border-purple-500/50 bg-gray-800/30 hover:bg-gray-800/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105"><div class="text-purple-400 mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-search h-8 w-8" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m21 21-4.34-4.34"></path><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"></circle></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Plate To VIN</h3><p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Convert license plates to VIN numbers with our advanced lookup technology and database.</p></div><div class="group p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-700 hover:border-purple-500/50 bg-gray-800/30 hover:bg-gray-800/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105"><div class="text-purple-400 mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-shield h-8 w-8" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z"></path></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Stolen Vehicle Check</h3><p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Verify if a vehicle has been reported stolen with real-time database lookups and alerts.</p></div><div class="group p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-700 hover:border-purple-500/50 bg-gray-800/30 hover:bg-gray-800/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105"><div class="text-purple-400 mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-clipboard-check h-8 w-8" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="8" height="4" x="8" y="2" rx="1" ry="1"></rect><path d="M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2"></path><path d="m9 14 2 2 4-4"></path></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Vehicle Inspection</h3><p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Access periodic roadworthiness and emissions inspection records (MOT, TÜV, TK/EK) from European countries.</p></div><div class="group p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-700 hover:border-purple-500/50 bg-gray-800/30 hover:bg-gray-800/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105"><div class="text-purple-400 mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-list h-8 w-8" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M3 5h.01"></path><path d="M3 12h.01"></path><path d="M3 19h.01"></path><path d="M8 5h13"></path><path d="M8 12h13"></path><path d="M8 19h13"></path></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Vehicle Listing</h3><p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Access comprehensive vehicle listings with detailed specifications, pricing, and availability.</p></div><div class="group p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-700 hover:border-purple-500/50 bg-gray-800/30 hover:bg-gray-800/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105"><div class="text-purple-400 mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-camera h-8 w-8" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M13.997 4a2 2 0 0 1 1.76 1.05l.486.9A2 2 0 0 0 18.003 7H20a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v9a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V9a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h1.997a2 2 0 0 0 1.759-1.048l.489-.904A2 2 0 0 1 10.004 4z"></path><circle cx="12" cy="13" r="3"></circle></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Vehicle Photos</h3><p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">High-quality vehicle images and photo galleries for enhanced user experiences.</p></div><div class="group p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-700 hover:border-purple-500/50 bg-gray-800/30 hover:bg-gray-800/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105"><div class="text-purple-400 mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-credit-card h-8 w-8" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="20" height="14" x="2" y="5" rx="2"></rect><line x1="2" x2="22" y1="10" y2="10"></line></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Vehicle Payments</h3><p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Calculate monthly payments, financing options, and payment estimates for any vehicle.</p></div><div class="group p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-700 hover:border-purple-500/50 bg-gray-800/30 hover:bg-gray-800/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105"><div class="text-purple-400 mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-calculator h-8 w-8" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="16" height="20" x="4" y="2" rx="2"></rect><line x1="8" x2="16" y1="6" y2="6"></line><line x1="16" x2="16" y1="14" y2="18"></line><path d="M16 10h.01"></path><path d="M12 10h.01"></path><path d="M8 10h.01"></path><path d="M12 14h.01"></path><path d="M8 14h.01"></path><path d="M12 18h.01"></path><path d="M8 18h.01"></path></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Vehicle Valuation</h3><p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Vehicle price information and yearly market value estimations based on depreciation analysis.</p></div><div class="group p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-700 hover:border-purple-500/50 bg-gray-800/30 hover:bg-gray-800/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105"><div class="text-purple-400 mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chart-column h-8 w-8" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M3 3v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16"></path><path d="M18 17V9"></path><path d="M13 17V5"></path><path d="M8 17v-3"></path></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Mileage History</h3><p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Track vehicle odometer readings and mileage history over time for maintenance and verification purposes.</p></div></div></div></section><section class="py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto"><div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center"><div><h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Simple API Integration in<span class="text-purple-400"> Minutes</span></h2><p class="text-xl text-gray-400 mb-8 leading-relaxed">RESTful APIs with comprehensive documentation, SDKs, and examples. Get automotive data integrated into your application quickly.</p><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-center space-x-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check h-5 w-5 text-green-400 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-gray-300">RESTful API with JSON responses</span></div><div class="flex items-center space-x-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check h-5 w-5 text-green-400 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-gray-300">SDKs for popular programming languages</span></div><div class="flex items-center space-x-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check h-5 w-5 text-green-400 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-gray-300">Real-time data updates</span></div><div class="flex items-center space-x-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check h-5 w-5 text-green-400 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-gray-300">99.9% uptime SLA</span></div></div></div><div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-700"><div class="flex items-center space-x-2 mb-4"><div class="flex space-x-2"><div class="w-3 h-3 bg-red-500 rounded-full"></div><div class="w-3 h-3 bg-yellow-500 rounded-full"></div><div class="w-3 h-3 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></div></div><span class="text-sm text-gray-500 ml-4">terminal</span></div><div class="font-mono text-sm"><div class="text-gray-500">$ curl -X GET \</div><div class="text-purple-400 mt-1">  "https://api.carapi.dev/v1/vin-decode/1HGBH41JXMN109186?token=YOUR_API_KEY"</div><div class="text-gray-500 mt-4">{</div><div class="text-green-400 ml-4">"make": "Honda",</div><div class="text-green-400 ml-4">"model": "Civic",</div><div class="text-green-400 ml-4">"year": 2021,</div><div class="text-green-400 ml-4">"engine": "1.5L Turbo"</div><div class="text-gray-500">}</div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="pricing" class="py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-gray-800/50"><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto"><div class="text-center mb-16"><h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Simple, Transparent Pricing</h2><p class="text-xl text-gray-400">Choose the plan that fits your needs</p></div><div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto"><div class="relative p-8 rounded-2xl border transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 border-gray-700 bg-gray-800/30 hover:border-gray-600"><div class="text-center mb-8"><h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Free</h3><div class="mb-4"><span class="text-4xl font-bold">Free</span></div><p class="text-gray-400">Perfect for testing and small projects</p></div><ul class="space-y-4 mb-8">